{"tid":2462641,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"Netflix高價買下中國電影《真‧三國無雙》, 但依然對香港本土電影冷淡","createTime":"2021-03-26T06:30:00.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-26T06:56:29.000Z","uid":134071,"like":9,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"1325e5cbfe82d810b714eeb34b32898f79368a18","tid":2462641,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T06:30:00.000Z","msg":"Netflix而家好少購買香港本土電影, 就算買, 出價都比電視台更低.<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2452965/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2452965/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n不過, Netflix購買大陸電影同中港合拍片就活躍得多.  <br />\nNetflix剛出高價買下古天樂有份主演既中港合拍片《真‧三國無雙》, 價錢仲係破記錄既高價.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/am730hk/posts/3950932934945764\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fam730hk%2Fposts%2F3950932934945764&d=eMoIgPJs71q5KSiTXOS1Gma%2FpyP0knsd4enDGc0qzPM%3D&h=3d5867f0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/am730hk/posts/3950932934945764</a><br />\n<br />\nam730<br />\n <br />\n30分鐘  &middot;<br />\n改編自同名經典遊戲、<strong>真人版《真‧三國無雙》雖然仍未上映，但Netflix已購買了電影版權</strong>，並安排於暑假期間，在海外地區陸續上架。據聞Netflix今次是看準《真‧三國無雙》在全球擁有眾多Fans，看片後亦非常喜歡，因此以<strong>破華片紀錄購買版權。</strong>"},{"pid":"5326db1f0a2c26c35d00c340e8341b810d4efc66","tid":2462641,"uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T06:30:27.000Z","msg":"Netflix都買左《葉問4：完結篇》美國網絡版權, 但就無理香港本土電影. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://whatsnewonnetflix.com/usa/1907968/ip-man-4-the-finale-2019\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwhatsnewonnetflix.com%2Fusa%2F1907968%2Fip-man-4-the-finale-2019&d=eMoIgPJs71q5KSiTXOS1Gma%2FpyP0knsd4enDGc0qzPM%3D&h=cc88d01c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://whatsnewonnetflix.com/usa/1907968/ip-man-4-the-finale-2019</a><br />\n<br />\n陳偉霆大陸爛片《侍神令》, 亦比Netflix高價買入. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a hre